It includes age-appropriate language to help you talk about the upcoming celebratory weekend with children between the ages of 7 and 11 (key stage 2 in England).  The pack also includes tasks that will help children to write, learn and explore more about what takes place as part of a coronation.   The news articles include reading comprehension questions which can be used to check your child’s understanding. Answers are also included in the pack. Looking for more resources to celebrate the upcoming coronation? Check out this handy Coronation Acrostic Poem Template! Or, for more child-friendly news stories and activities, visit Twinkl NewsRoom.
